id.comment: Select stmt such that Uses (stmt, variable)

query.querystr: stmt s; assign a; variable v; Select s such that Uses (s, v) pattern a (v, _"0"_)

id.comment: Select assign such that Uses (assign, variable)

query.querystr: assign a; variable v; Select a such that Uses (a, v) pattern a (_, _"xx1"_)

id.comment: Select assign such that Uses (assign, variable) but doesn't exsit

query.querystr: assign a; variable v; Select a such that Uses (a, v) pattern a (v, _)

id.comment: Select print such that Uses (print, variable)

query.querystr: print pn; assign a; variable v; Select pn such that Uses (pn, v) pattern a (v, _"100"_)
